OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FSome early brightness in the
OL,6,Ffar east, otherwise a cloudy day with
OL,7,Foccasional rain and drizzle. The rain
OL,8,Fturning heavy at times, especially
OL,9,Flater. Fog patches forming, and winds
OL,10,Fstrengthening.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FWet
OL,13,Fand windy for a time on Wednesday with
OL,14,Fscattered showers following on
OL,15,FThursday, before turning drier and
OL,16,Fbrighter on Friday. Feeling warmer
OL,17,Fthan of late, especially in any
OL,18,Fsunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
